{"id":"99695ab9a81de419aed7584834afd86e0677166de5f4853f87ffa5e660e0603c","item_id":"1c23620abd:0","text":"有关获取支持的一般信息，请参阅"}
{"id":"d7e5ec2a5626cc51b21261df60261c543419382a1c8feefa41225d45969c5c54","item_id":"1c23620abd:1","text":"Getting Support（获取支持）"}
{"id":"2c0560d6168d330b1a47ae7cc25f66051b42f3f9026a2a07f252b5e1d44d2acb","item_id":"1c23620abd:2","text":"页面。"}
{"id":"0c14e97d21883ba341c55b4a8d8029777efc61de49be0acc35f4450efe56bdfe","item_id":"1c23620abd:3","text":"Reproducing Issues/Bugs（复现问题/错误）"}
{"id":"71680c7025535ec480cde35a8cd2f2e259c482f78b31e729b7a3054ebdc826c1","item_id":"1c23620abd:4","text":"报告问题或错误时，我们通常需要一种复现该问题的方法。这通常意味着我们需要查看你的文件/资产。"}
{"id":"28a20c7b25e07f5d05595fff455bfdd537fca299c395e1cd0ca72275f2f66f47","item_id":"1c23620abd:5","text":"在 RfB 中，有一个方便的 Package Scene（打包场景）按钮，可用于将文件打包在一起，以便发送给 RenderMan Support。"}
{"id":"b4d043ce28bacd9879658d5adb4f552a8d489e2accb4a285fb48239ff896e012","item_id":"1c23620abd:6","text":"Debug Logging（调试日志）"}
{"id":"d83a47805fc89773ffb4f5a848c4eeb33290ac13d734da530d549e41e6ddd560","item_id":"1c23620abd:7","text":"对于崩溃问题，RfB 可以把渲染会话记录到 debug python file（调试 Python 文件）中。要开始记录日志，请在 render properties（渲染属性）选项卡中启用 Debug Logging，如下图所示。"}
{"id":"3b170b9975911d8c37557c837564fb274a75c8de02528690ef43fc3cde1708ef","item_id":"1c23620abd:8","text":"此选项必须在"}
{"id":"6db7d803e74f1ffa7d8f5adc0bf95b3e15bf4c8373fffadf546227cc6c6742cb","item_id":"1c23620abd:9","text":"之前"}
{"id":"5985a58208d575804d7277a86a953fcf8a1593861c96681360121fb43d413c48","item_id":"1c23620abd:10","text":"渲染开始前启用"}
{"id":"11b8b6d6e411e1af35f0d7422fa0c3a9ada15d9cdf664f60d9b9167926c2d85b","item_id":"1c23620abd:11","text":"日志会放在当前 blend 文件所在的同一目录中（带有"}
{"id":"c51266508942a7cd35a0f816fffa8c97afa1a10f3f9abb3f8fc27a93afd3966b","item_id":"1c23620abd:12","text":".debug.py"}
{"id":"1322efa3b028437dbdfceda17efba64c744607866116a1812df44484d81709e0","item_id":"1c23620abd:13","text":"文件扩展名）。请确保当前 blend 文件所在文件夹可写。"}
{"id":"3b9f829a62e69daeb0632c9f3177436af040c789a13e8b639abc09bb93f9ab64","item_id":"1c23620abd:14","text":"日志文件可能占用大量磁盘空间，尤其是较重的场景。生成完日志文件后，应确保关闭此选项。"}
{"id":"d4f85276c67c097ecffbfea55ecc3a0f56f48724d91afccaca275c9e31b72826","item_id":"1c23620abd:15","text":"Package Scene（打包场景）"}
{"id":"da15b22aacedcdaaa95b5f1faa9de3bab041a9c857aece6a00c3a56ef2c5364c","item_id":"1c23620abd:16","text":"要打包场景，请在 viewport（视口）中按 'n' 键。这应会打开侧边菜单。"}
{"id":"cf292e84dc6c0e662b7593f7868bb52e1bd2f94723c1c42e65c33270dc2cbcac","item_id":"1c23620abd:17","text":"接下来，点击 Renderman 选项卡。"}
{"id":"80a20cc77d50fde84d4c2275ea8a22d1ff12862dbc5fbe75b8f7e358799850e7","item_id":"1c23620abd:18","text":"在 Utilities 下，点击 Package Scene 按钮。这会打开文件浏览器。"}
{"id":"ff40ce54dd35029acbeb2b9914a53539b855dc8ab55c36b04c19245e0f8b2eb8","item_id":"1c23620abd:19","text":"选择一个新的目录或已有的空目录，然后点击 Package Scene。该目录现在应包含一个新的 ZIP 文件，你随后可以把它随错误报告一起发送。"}
{"id":"367431fd664bb686d9ffd213339b1382fd8e1509c21fcdc87fabf68bd16f1333","item_id":"1c23620abd:20","text":"Options（选项）："}
{"id":"9e3a6c73297b4b9e918abef93dc935e7b6657e422aff2b8d0ae43e25f63e7e82","item_id":"1c23620abd:21","text":"Include Blend File（包含 Blend 文件）"}
{"id":"e80c56bf6f07f98b84f1cf8e124716645a9f220679d2cab3c6540e6537ed9580","item_id":"1c23620abd:22","text":"：这会把 .blend 文件包含在 ZIP 包中"}
{"id":"96c5af3b7269765ea51e4ee01fc010e59b223172e9a7e926bfc62a032d587b74","item_id":"1c23620abd:23","text":"Include Debug Log（包含调试日志）："}
{"id":"4678b48bfcc89b68d4ebc7a2d35294c2d42b19bb0037e1d89fb69a9c7c9adb3f","item_id":"1c23620abd:24","text":"如果存在日志 .debug.py 文件，则将其包含在 ZIP 包中。"}
{"id":"9b36dddbefafc63fb574e5782a6d7d884ce0ed1faf819cadbb99ec3e3c0dbc9d","item_id":"1c23620abd:25","text":"Use RenderMan Textures（使用 RenderMan 纹理）："}
{"id":"d3d60788dbad979638c578291c515bd012431ed1cf33dd2d2ce84ff4b2f2ac29","item_id":"1c23620abd:26","text":"这会将场景中的所有纹理文件路径替换为等效的 RenderMan .tex 纹理。"}
